\section*{Glossary}

\begin{itemize}
    \item \textbf{Molecular Graph}: A labeled graph representing atoms and bonds
    \item \textbf{Resonance Structure}: An integer assignment of bond orders satisfying valence
    \item \textbf{Arrow Push}: Movement of one electron pair between resonance structures
    \item \textbf{Resonance Graph}: Graph whose vertices are resonance structures
    \item \textbf{Resonance Homology}: Homology groups of the resonance complex
    \item \textbf{Betti Number}: Dimension of a homology group
    \item \textbf{Ring Current}: Measure of electron circulation in a ring
    \item \textbf{NICS}: Nucleus-Independent Chemical Shift (aromaticity measure)
    \item \textbf{Fukui Index}: Reactivity measure from frontier orbitals
    \item \textbf{Graph Laplacian}: Matrix \( L = D - A \) for spectral analysis
